additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Keep reach out of children and pets. Adult use only. Please read the safety and precautionary text on device pack before use. Do not swallow. Liquid may be harmful if swallowed and enters airways. Use in well-ventilated areas. Switch off before inserting refills. Once opened do not store refill out of the device. Do not leave unattended. Store at room temperature. Keep away from heat, hot surfaces, sparks, open flames and other ignition sources. No smoking. Keep out of reach of children. People suffering from perfume sensitivity should be cautious when using this product.

description: Air Wick Essential Mist Happiness contains a fragrance infused with essential oils that can help your feelings of joy and bliss.  1 refill lasts up to 45 daysFragrance infused with essential oils that can help your feelings of joy and blissPineapple, peach and wild mint fragrance
